# Run all tests with coverage
mvn clean test jacoco:report

# Run only unit tests
mvn test

# Run integration tests
mvn failsafe:integration-test

# Run with specific profile
mvn test -Pcoverage

# Generate detailed reports
mvn site

# Check code quality
mvn checkstyle:check spotbugs:check pmd:check



Sample Test Report Structure

target/
├── site/
│   ├── jacoco/          # Code coverage reports
│   ├── checkstyle/      # Code quality reports  
│   ├── spotbugs/        # Bug detection reports
│   └── pmd/            # Code analysis reports
├── surefire-reports/    # Unit test reports
├── failsafe-reports/    # Integration test reports
└── jacoco.exec         # Coverage execution data